# --- Coding Bugs (emerging) ---
[] Anchor inconsistency in DrawCage

# --- Architecture / Design Bugs (emerging) ---
[] Entity position semantics (head vs body vs center) are inconsistent
[] Rendering code mutates or implies gameplay state (animation vs logic)
[] Collision logic is inconsistent across entities and world objects
[] Entity data is passed by value instead of by ownership intent (const / mut)
